dc_description_s: This line data layer represents hydrography for Outagamie County, Wisconsin in 2014.[This dataset includes the navigable stream layer identifying the location of all non-navigable and navigable water within Outagamie County. It is a county-wide file including all USGS designated navigable waterways and all non-navigable waterways. Also included is the Display water lines and water polygons. Those are used for mapping purposes only include the major waterways within the County.]
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For access to the most current data available, please visit: https://data-ocgis.opendata.arcgis.com/
